                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.6363 Manchuria/156: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-03-30T14:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 30, 1935—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>53. Your 69, March 29, 11 a.m. Department is inclined in general to agree with
                    the views and to approve suggestion for possible future action outlined in
                    paragraphs 1 and 2 but will await further report from you before issuing
                    instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
